title: Cuisinart Green Gourmet Electric 14-Inch Skillet (CSK-250) Demo Video
description: Cuisinart presents a skillet that's good for you and a little easier on the environment! The interior of our GreenGourmet® Electric Skillet is premium Cuisinart Ceramica® nonstick, a petroleum-free ceramic-based cooking surface that contains no PTFE or PFOA. This smart nonstick lets you sear, fry, griddle, simmer or braise with little or no oil or butter, and cleans up in record time!
